data.description: Welcome to 202 W West St located in the heart and historic district of El Campo, TX. This warm and inviting home sits on a large corner lot and boasts beautiful mature trees. As you enter the home, you will find 3 bedrooms, 2 updated bathrooms, a formal living and dining room, a nice kitchen with granite counter tops, breakfast dining, and a second living area that could be a family room or a game room. Enjoy peaceful evenings on your back porch in the fully fenced backyard. There are so many memories to be made in this beautiful home- it's a must see!
